transcripts.text: He grew up in a mansion in New York City.  She grew up here in Oklahoma.  He got millions from his dad's real estate empire.  Her dad ended up a janitor.  He scammed students at his for-profit school.  She got debts forgiven for students who were scammed.  When someone shows you who they are, believe them.  Trump's life taught him how to get rich on the backs of others.  Elizabeth Warren will be a president who works for you.  I'm Elizabeth Warren, and I approve this message.  Thank you.
